so much for coming.

00:51:47.270 --> 00:51:50.140
Thank you for coming
and talking with us.

00:51:50.140 --> 00:51:52.790
It's been really, really
cool to have you here.

00:51:52.790 --> 00:51:53.914
ADAM BRAUN: Thank you guys.

